    <previous>Evaṃ vutte verañjo brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca – jeṭṭho bhavaṃ gotamo, seṭṭho bhavaṃ gotamo. Abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama, abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama! Seyyathāpi, bho gotama, nikkujjitaṃ </previous>
  </note>
  <note line="38" original="sandhāgāre (ka.)" reference-line="24" id="5">
